- Uses glass morphism styling with `var(--bg-elevated)` background
- Currently only shows the post title as placeholder content

---

### Key Integration Points

1. **State management:** PostCards uses `postIdSettings` (line 43) and `setPostIdSettings` to toggle modal visibility
2. **Click handler:** `handleClickSettings` (line 312) toggles the modal open/closed
3. **Click-outside detection:** useEffect (lines 438-449) closes modal when clicking outside modalRef
4. **Modal ref:** `const modalRef = useRef(null)` attached to the modal div for click detection
5. **Animation:** Uses Framer Motion `<motion.div>` for smooth open/close transitions

This is the perfect place to integrate ShareMenu as one of the setting options!

